defense: 1 if one or both states in the dyad  a defense pact with the othadher state in the dyad
neutrality: 1 if one or both states in the dyad had a neutrality pact with the other state in the dyad
nonaggression: 1 if one or both states in the dyad had a non-aggression pact with the other state in the dyad
entente: 1 if one or both states in the dyad had an understanding that consultations with the other state in the dyad would take place if a crisis occurred
